Question: Are both the ball to the right of the other balls and the black helmet made of plastic?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n146522.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='ball')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='balls')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'no'")
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='helmet')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX2)
ANSWER2=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the helmet?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER2} == 'black' else 'no'")
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
